init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm in my next life, watching myself live it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But then you began watching a beautiful girl.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You were a really good guy this time, and she was a happy girl who turned into a happy woman.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: And for a while, that was true.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You screamed at the screen in agony and despair, and the next you simply smiled and left her.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Calm down," he said, and you turned around to see a tall skinny man in a black suit.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "That is interesting, but the next time I see her she may be married or have children or..."
